---
@version: [current]
@description: Format date input using custom formatter.
@lot: string $pattern = '%Y%-%M%-%D% %~h%:%m%:%s%'
@example: |
  $date = (new Date('[[e]]echo date('Y-m-d H:i:s');[[/e]]'))->pattern('%Y%/%M%/%D%');
@result: |
  $date = '[[e]]echo (new Date(date('Y-m-d H:i:s')))->pattern('%Y%/%M%/%D%');[[/e]]';
...

Supported date pattern:

Pattern | Description
------- | -----------
`%year%` | Get year number.
`%month%` | Get month number (from 01 to 12).
`%day%` | Get day number (from 01 to 31).
`%hour%` | Get hour 24 number (from 00 to 24).
`%minute%` | Get minute number (from 00 to 60).
`%second%` | Get second number (from 00 to 60).
`%noon%` | `AM` or `PM`.
`%week%` | Get day number in a week (from 01 to 07).
`%zone%` | Get current time zone.
`%~M%` | Get month name.
`%~D%` | Get day name.
`%~h%` | Alias for `%hour%`.
`%Y%` | Alias for `%year%`.
`%M%` | Alias for `%month%`.
`%D%` | Alias for `%day%`.
`%h%` | Get hour 12 number (from 00 to 12).
`%m%` | Alias for `%minute%`.
`%s%` | Alias for `%second%`.
`%N%` | Alias for `%noon%`.
`%W%` | Alias for `%week%`.
`%Z%` | Alias for `%zone%`.